The paper focuses on deep-networks-based hashing for large-scale image retrieval, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a novel deep policy hashing architecture that utilizes listwise supervision, which involves learning to rank and optimization, indicating that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), multimedia (cs.MM), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
